<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="1Apr1925"><font color="red">1 April 1925</font> <i>Letters III</i> (to Lily Bollach): (large black pencil) I want to give you some MS next week if I am better but I am not well enough yet &mdash; the MS I told you of &hellip; Please write with a heavy black pencil. I cannot distinguish one word of print or pen but can pencil with a magnifying glass </div>
